author: Sheyna 🧚🏾‍♀️
text: She explained all relationships have hardships but what makes the relationship work is growth. During those fallouts, thoughts shouldn’t be of replacements but what have you learned… all in all, she said she is happy she chose her forever mate & glad he had the same mindset.

author: Sheyna 🧚🏾‍♀️
text: She went on to explain that many would never cut off their parents, children, family etc. so why would divorce be an option for your spouse?!? She explained she didn’t always like him (hubby) & they’ve sometimes slept in other areas of the home but they never threw in the towel

author: Sheyna 🧚🏾‍♀️
text: I will never 4get what an elder lady told me at the nail salon over 10yrs ago. She was a married woman for over 40yrs & the main reason they never divorced was bc they never saw it as an option. She explained marriage is a relationship no different than one w/parents, kids etc.
